{"tid":1787460,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球訂戶最多 YouTuber   「PewDiePie」宣佈明年暫別","createTime":"2019-12-18T02:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T11:04:32.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"354f0e394aa66aa3794f5aa8f1e484ff87e10dba","tid":1787460,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:45:46.000Z","msg":"現時全球唯一在 YouTube 擁有過億訂戶的 PewDiePie，在剛過去的週末上載批評 YouTube 新政策的影片時，同時宣佈會在 2020 年暫時退出 YouTube。這名來自瑞典的 YouTuber 原名 Felix Kjellberg，以分享打機影片起家，現時訂戶人數達 1.02 億，點擊率超過 240 億，不但是全球最紅，亦曾經是全球收入最高的 YouTuber。<br />\n<br />\nPewDiePie 在影片中表示「明年我要從 YouTube 休息一陣子，我提前宣佈是因為已經下定決心。我感到疲累，不知道網民是否明白」。至於具體原因，PewDiePie 表示會稍後解釋，不過他早在今年 8 月已經暗示會暫時休息。這名全球最紅 YouTuber 近年曾經因為有關種族主義和反猶太言論而引發爭議，早前則因為評論大陸和香港反修例運動而被大陸當局封殺。<br />\n<br />\n來源：udn<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/t9-4eMdBejk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ft9-4eMdBejk&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BuvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=ba72f122\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/t9-4eMdBejk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/12/18/pewdiepie-away-from-youtube-and-take-a-rest-2020/life-tech/social-network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F12%2F18%2Fpewdiepie-away-from-youtube-and-take-a-rest-2020%2Flife-tech%2Fsocial-network%2F&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BuvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=1c8c7d3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/12/18/pewdiepie-away-from-youtube-and-take-a-rest-2020/life-tech/social-network/</a>"},{"pid":"4e85b9406813a6ad350fa0f732a8d5368e9c1050","tid":1787460,"uid":70472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:57:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RoFSqtrivFs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRoFSqtrivFs&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BuvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=17d2f45d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RoFSqtrivFs</a><br />\nPdp出左片屌鳩班報紙佬亂作fake news"},{"pid":"ac567b9ffde86a121821